text: Nickelodeon (commonly shortened to Nick) is a British and Irish pay television network launched on 1 September 1993, a localised version of the original US channel. In the United Kingdom, the channel is available on Sky, Virgin Media, and TalkTalk Plus TV. In Ireland, the channel is available on Virgin Media Ireland, Eir TV and Sky Ireland. It is the first Nickelodeon feed launched overseas. ==Programming== ==Notes== ==References== Category:Nickelodeon Category:British television channels Category:Irish culture Category:Irish television channels Category:1993 establishments in the United Kingdom
